<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy - Today" %>

<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6 px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Last updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      Today ("we", "our", or "us") operates the Today mobile application and website (the "Service").
      This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data
      when you use our Service.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-800">Account Information</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      When you create an account, we collect your email address and password. Your password is encrypted
      and stored securely.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-800">Todo Data</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      We collect and store the todo items you create, including their content, completion status, and
      associated metadata.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-800">Voice Recordings</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      When you use the voice command feature, we temporarily process audio recordings to convert them
      into todo items using AI technology. Audio recordings are not permanently stored and are deleted
      immediately after processing.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-700">
      <li>To provide and maintain our Service</li>
      <li>To manage your account and provide customer support</li>
      <li>To process voice commands and create todo items</li>
      <li>To improve and optimize our Service</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Microphone Access</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      The Today app requests access to your device's microphone solely for the purpose of recording
      voice commands to create todo items. We do not access your microphone for any other purpose.
      You can revoke microphone access at any time in your device settings.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal
      data. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure,
      and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to provide the Service and fulfill
      the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. You may delete your account at any time, which
      will remove all associated data from our systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">You have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-700">
      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Export your data</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      We use third-party AI services to process voice recordings and generate todo items. These services
      process your audio data according to their own privacy policies. Audio data is transmitted securely
      and is not stored by these services.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      Our Service is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect
      personal data from children under 13. If you become aware that a child has provided us with
      personal data, please contact us.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting
      the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
    </p>
  </section>
</div>
